### PublicLink HTTP tests

@base=http://localhost:8000
@json=application/json
@token=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create public link
POST {{base}}/api/public-links
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "file_id": 1,
  "expires_at": "2025-12-31"
}

### List public links
GET {{base}}/api/public-links
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View file via public link (no auth)
GET {{base}}/api/public-links/abc123
Accept: {{json}}

### Download via public link (no auth)
GET {{base}}/api/public-links/abc123/download

### Revoke link
POST {{base}}/api/public-links/1/revoke
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete link
DELETE {{base}}/api/public-links/1
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

